## 1. 授权范围（License Permissions）

在本许可证下，任何个人或组织均可**自由**获取、复制、修改、合并、发布、分发及再授权本软件及其文档，前提是遵守以下条款：

> Under this license, any individual or organization may freely obtain, copy, modify, merge, publish, distribute, and sublicense copies of this software and its documentation, provided that the following conditions are met:

### 1.1 署名要求（Attribution Requirement）

使用、修改或分发本软件时，必须**明确标注原作者 “SB Games Team” 或 “SB Games”**，并注明所有后续贡献者。

> The original authors ("SB Games Team" or "SB Games") and any subsequent contributors must be prominently credited.

### 1.2 开源再分发（Open Source Redistribution）

软件可以在相同的开源许可条款下自由共享、修改和再分发。**修改后的版本必须说明更改内容并保留本许可证。**

> This software may be freely shared, modified, and redistributed under the same open license terms. Modified versions must clearly indicate the changes made and retain this license.

### 1.3 共同著作权归属（Joint Copyright Ownership）

原作者与贡献者共同拥有修改版本的著作权，**修改行为不影响原作者的权利归属。**

> The original authors and any subsequent contributors both jointly own the copyright of modified versions of the software. Any modifications do not invalidate the original authorship claim.

### 1.4 责任归属（Liability Clause）

因使用、修改或分发**修改版本**所产生的任何法律或经济责任，**仅由修改者本人承担。**

> Any responsibility, including legal or financial, arising from the use, modification, or redistribution of modified versions shall solely rest on the modifying author.

