## 3. 特殊用途展示与间接盈利（Public Displays & Indirect Monetization）

如将本软件或其内容用于以下任一**公开展示或营利性行为**，须事先获得授权，并提供有效的**授权凭证**以示合规：

> If this software or its content is used in any of the following public or monetized scenarios, prior authorization is required, along with valid **proof of authorization**:

### 3.1 需要授权的情况（Authorization Required For）：

* 商业演讲、品牌展示、市场宣传；
* 以“社区版”“再制版”等名义重新发布并公开分发；
* 利用内容产生**间接收入**（如通过推荐链接、引流获利、展示性广告获益等）；
* 其他 SB Games Team 认定需要授权的使用场景。

> - Commercial presentations, brand displays, or promotional uses
> - Publishing modified or rebranded versions as "Community Edition" or similar
> - Indirect monetization, such as through affiliate links, traffic-based revenue, or ad-supported showcases
> - Any other use as deemed authorization-required by SB Games Team

